exists_mono
-----------

l1: $ F y ==> F y $ by ax
l2: $ G y ==> G y $ by ax
l3: $ F y , F y → G y ==> G y $ by imp_left [l1, l2]
l4: $ ∀ x (F x → G x) , F y ==> G y $ by all_left [l3]
l5: $ ∀ x (F x → G x) , F y ==> ∃ z G z $ by ex_right [l4]
l6: $ ∀ x (F x → G x) , ∃ y F y ==> ∃ z G z $ by ex_left [l5]
